      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KOORINGA EXPRESS (1) is a promising dog in the frame at six of 17 starts including six wins and was in the minors again latest (22.57) over 400m at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Drawn the fence and expected to go close. LORD EDDIE (4) missed the frame latest when fifth at Goulburn (25.70) but scored five back at this track (22.44). Returns to a course where he has performed well. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from five starts. Key runner on best form. ANGELIC ANGEL (3) boasts a strong record this course with seven wins and three minors from 17 tries. Missed the frame latest (30.47) when fifth over 520m at Wentworth Park in a Grade 5. Looks one of the chances. FANCY BELLA (8) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
